2500|$|The first {{partially}} {{free elections}} to the Verkhovna Rada and local councils of people's deputies were held on 4 March 1990. Although the Communist Party still remained in control, a [...] "Democratic Bloc" [...] {{was formed by}} numerous parties, including People's Movement of Ukraine (Rukh), <b>Helsinki</b> Watch <b>Committee</b> of Ukraine, Party of Greens of Ukraine, and many others.|$|R
